sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Application (Instrumentation: Prometheus Client Lib)
    participant P as Prometheus Server
    participant G as Grafana (UI)

    Note over A: Metrics generated internally (Prometheus format)
    A->>A: Collects Metrics (RAM)

    P->>A: HTTP GET /metrics (Pull)
    A-->>P: Returns Metrics (OpenMetrics/Text)

    Note over P: Storage (TSDB) and serving
    G->>P: Data Query (PromQL)
    P-->>G: Data for visualization
